<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="respond-v">respond <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /rɪ'spɒnd/    美 /rɪ'spɑːnd/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-reply">1.★ <strong>回答 (reply)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>respond to</strong> a letter 
回信</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>respond with a smile 
报以微笑</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>When asked about the company’s future, the director <strong>responded that</strong> he remained optimistic. 
当被问到公司的未来时，经理回答说他依然乐观。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-react">2.★ <strong>响应；有反应 (react)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Knowing basic first-aid techniques will help you respond quickly to emergencies. 
懂得基本的急救技能将有助于你对紧急情况做出迅速反应。</p><footer>2013 福建</footer></div></div>